{"thag10.6:0.1":"Theragatha 10.6 ","thag10.6:0.2":"Dasakanipata ","thag10.6:0.3":"Pathamavagga ","thag10.6:0.4":"Vangantaputtaupasenattheragatha ","thag10.6:1.1":"“Vivittam appanigghosam, ","thag10.6:1.2":"valamiganisevitam; ","thag10.6:1.3":"Seve senasanam bhikkhu, ","thag10.6:1.4":"patisallanakarana. ","thag10.6:2.1":"Sankarapunja ahatva, ","thag10.6:2.2":"susana rathiyahi ca; ","thag10.6:2.3":"Tato sanghatikam katva, ","thag10.6:2.4":"lukham dhareyya civaram. ","thag10.6:3.1":"Nicam manam karitvana, ","thag10.6:3.2":"sapadanam kula kulam; ","thag10.6:3.3":"Pindikaya care bhikkhu, ","thag10.6:3.4":"guttadvaro susamvuto. ","thag10.6:4.1":"Lukhenapi va santusse, ","thag10.6:4.2":"nannam patthe rasam bahum; ","thag10.6:4.3":"Rasesu anugiddhassa, ","thag10.6:4.4":"jhane na ramati mano. ","thag10.6:5.1":"Appiccho ceva santuttho, ","thag10.6:5.2":"pavivitto vase muni; ","thag10.6:5.3":"Asamsattho gahatthehi, ","thag10.6:5.4":"anagarehi cubhayam. ","thag10.6:6.1":"Yatha jalo va mugo va, ","thag10.6:6.2":"attanam dassaye tatha; ","thag10.6:6.3":"Nativelam sambhaseyya, ","thag10.6:6.4":"sanghamajjhamhi pandito. ","thag10.6:7.1":"Na so upavade kanci, ","thag10.6:7.2":"upaghatam vivajjaye; ","thag10.6:7.3":"Samvuto patimokkhasmim, ","thag10.6:7.4":"mattannu cassa bhojane. ","thag10.6:8.1":"Suggahitanimittassa, ","thag10.6:8.2":"cittassuppadakovido; ","thag10.6:8.3":"Samatham anuyunjeyya, ","thag10.6:8.4":"kalena ca vipassanam. ","thag10.6:9.1":"Viriyasataccasampanno, ","thag10.6:9.2":"yuttayogo sada siya; ","thag10.6:9.3":"Na ca appatva dukkhantam, ","thag10.6:9.4":"vissasam eyya pandito. ","thag10.6:10.1":"Evam viharamanassa, ","thag10.6:10.2":"suddhikamassa bhikkhuno; ","thag10.6:10.3":"Khiyanti asava sabbe, ","thag10.6:10.4":"nibbutincadhigacchati”ti. ","thag10.6:10.5":"… Upaseno vangantaputto thero …. "}